reviewText: Liked the movie and William Holden and the story.

Not a killer script, but it's so charming that I had to jump online and get a copy.

Newlyweds traverse the delicate proposition of growing a marriage amidst a disapproving father.  The husband is adorable as he strives to please his wife and she him except when it comes to a particular chair. Sweet and endearing.  This film is a hidden treasure!
